com.friendlyreminder.application.person

Class Contact

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.friendlyreminder.application.person.Person
      • com.friendlyreminder.application.person.Contact

  • @Entity
public class Contact
extends Person
    Class that represents a contact. It contains a list of CommunicationEvents - This class is saved to Relational Database according to Hibernate annotations - The event list in the contact is sorted by one of CommunicationEventSortingStrategy strategies
